 * - ResolveExport(name, state): Retrieve output fields with caching
 * - ResolveDiagnostic(name, nx, ny, nz): Register/retrieve diagnostic fields
 * - MarkModified(name, state): Signal device-side field updates
 * - Input/output field name mapping via YAML config
 *
